## Resources.ICandidateValue interface

Interface for a candidate value that can be collected and indexed. Candidate values are normalized JSON values that can be shared across multiple resource candidates to reduce duplication.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export interface ICandidateValue extends Collections.ICollectible<CandidateValueKey, CandidateValueIndex> 
```
**Extends:** Collections.ICollectible&lt;[CandidateValueKey](./ts-res.candidatevaluekey.md)<!-- -->, [CandidateValueIndex](./ts-res.candidatevalueindex.md)<!-- -->&gt;
